data.description: 55+ community You own the land. HOA fees only 40.25/month. Don't miss out on this 1981 mobile home in one of the most desirable communities in Lake County! An assumable mortgage maybe available at 3.18%, see if you can qualify. This 2 bedroom/2 bath is to say the least a must have. Call for a showing as soon as you can. It is occupied and must have 24-hour notice. Sold as is, the owner is leaving to Louisianna with his family.  This community features 2 pools (indoor and outdoor), large patio for social activities, fishing on Lake Frances, shuffleboard courts, billiards room, large clubhouse, and library.  This location gives you easy golf cart access to a large grocery store and many great restaurants downtown Tavares, along with beautiful sunsets on Lake Dora and Lake Frances!   Here is your chance to own your own property. Check this one out today!
